    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A vertical column of divine &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} roars down from the heavens in a location you specify. Each creature in a 10-foot-radius, 40-foot-high &amp;Reference[cylinder]{cylinder} centered on a point within range must make a &amp;Reference[dex]{Dexterity} saving throw. A creature takes 4d6 &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage and 4d6 &amp;Reference[radiant]{radiant} damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage or the &amp;Reference[radiant]{radiant} damage (your choice) increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 5th.</p>\n</div>",
